OL,3,CMeet Newport's growing Kerala
OL,4,Ccommunity as they celebrate Onam
OL,6,FHundreds of people from Newport's
OL,7,FKerala community have gathered this
OL,8,Fweekend to celebrate the harvest
OL,9,Ffestival of Onam.
OL,11,FThe community has grown greatly since
OL,12,Fthe early 2000s, from just a handful
OL,13,Fof families to more than 1000 members
OL,14,Fin Newport alone.
OL,16,FNewport Kerala Community, an
OL,17,Forganisation set up to support and
OL,18,Fcelebrate Kerala's cultural traditions
OL,19,Fin Newport, say many members have
OL,20,Ftravelled from the southern Indian
OL,21,Fstate to live and work in Wales.
