OL,3,CMeet Newport's growing Kerala
OL,4,Ccommunity as they celebrate Onam
OL,6,F"It has grown so fast," says Rio
OL,7,FJohny, the organisation's Secretary.
OL,9,F"Covid is one of the reasons, where we
OL,10,Fhad a shortage in healthcare, and most
OL,11,Fof our community members got an
OL,12,Fopportunity to serve this nation, so
OL,13,Fthey came and they are doing their
OL,14,Fpart as healthcare workers.
OL,16,F"That gave us an opportunity to settle
OL,17,Fdown and become as a big community...
OL,18,FAlways looking as a community to
OL,19,Fdeliver something best for the
OL,20,Fgenerations, something best for the
OL,21,FWelsh (and) the UK."
