OL,3,CMeet Newport's growing Kerala
OL,4,Ccommunity as they celebrate Onam
OL,6,FThis weekend's celebrations saw a
OL,7,Fpacked schedule of music and dance at
OL,8,FSt Julian's School in Newport, with
OL,9,Flocal Senedd Members and the new
OL,10,FHealth Secretary Jeremy Miles in
OL,11,Fattendance.
OL,13,FFood is another tradition that is an
OL,14,Fimportant part of the festival, with
OL,15,Fthe vegetarian Sadya meal comprising
OL,16,Fof a rich variety of dishes served on
OL,17,Fa banana leaf.
