OL,3,CMeet Newport's growing Kerala
OL,4,Ccommunity as they celebrate Onam
OL,6,FIt is this type of tradition and
OL,7,Fheritage that Newport Kerala Community
OL,8,FPresident Joshy Thomas wants to
OL,9,Fpreserve, as well as celebrating the
OL,10,Fcommunity's integration in Wales.
OL,12,F"We wanted to continue (that) our
OL,13,Fchildren learn, and they want to
OL,14,Fperform and they want to grow (in)
OL,15,Fconfidence," says Joshy Thomas.
OL,17,F"In 2004 when I came to the UK, I
OL,18,Fnever thought I'm going to survive.
